"The bullet points listed below are excerpts from this user's long-term "
"memory (persistent memos). Use them as background information about the "
"user. However, always prioritize newly provided information in the "
"conversation, and if it contradicts older information, adopt the latest "
"information.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

